text: Parshin (Russian: Паршин) (feminine: Parshina) is a Russian-language surname. It may refer to: *Aleksandr Parshin, Russian footballer *, Russian mathematician, the namesake of the terms "Parshin chain" and "Parshin's conjecture" *Denis Parshin, Russian ice hockey player *Georgy Parshin, Soviet World War II pilot, twice Hero of the Soviet Union *Nikolai Parshin, Soviet footballer *Lana Parshina, Russian-American journalist and filmmaker *Daria Parshina, Russian swimmer Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Parshin
